| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2694 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b521270a-dc4b-5e71-b5ca-9aaab10d796f"
